    "stage": "Understanding ideas",
    "stageLabel": "理解篇",
    "unitNumber": 1,
    "unitTheme": "The secrets of happiness",
    "bookId": "g7b",
    "bookLabel": "七年级下册",
    "bookShortLabel": "7下",
    "bookOrder": 210,
    "summary": "从《查理和巧克力工厂》里的家庭故事，理解“贫穷但充满爱”的幸福感。"
  },
  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "u3-article-s1",
      "text": "I put down Charlie and the Chocolate Factory.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-article-p1",
      "tr": "我放下了《查理和巧克力工厂》这本书。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语",
      "d": "'put down' 是动词短语，意为'放下'。书名作为宾语。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/n4zCeUFJbDpWFUf7pw6Kee.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-article-s2",
      "text": "But I kept going over the exciting story in my mind.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-article-p1",
      "tr": "但我脑海中不断回味着这个激动人心的故事。",
      "g": "连词 + 主语 + 谓语 + 宾语 + 状语",
      "d": "'keep doing sth' 表示'持续做某事'。'go over' 意为'复习、重温'。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/JMsoS6ztyfkNoRq7rnPTFJ.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-article-s3",
      "text": "The book was full of magic.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-article-p1",
      "tr": "这本书充满了魔力。",
      "g": "主语 + 系动词 + 表语",
      "d": "'be full of' 是固定搭配，意为'充满...'。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/uoPCvG6tDh4hPYcnxFyQaN.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-article-s4",
      "text": "But Charlie’s happy family was the most magical part of the story.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-article-p1",
      "tr": "但查理幸福的家庭是故事中最神奇的部分。",
      "g": "主语 + 系动词 + 表语",
      "d": "'the most magical' 是形容词最高级形式，修饰 'part'。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/m5bFJ7jAMKNbqxQPurCSWW.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-article-s5",
      "text": "Charlie’s home was a small house at the side of a big town.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-article-p2",
      "tr": "查理的家是位于大城镇边缘的一座小房子。",
      "g": "主语 + 系动词 + 表语 + 地点状语",
      "d": "'at the side of' 表示'在...旁边/边缘'。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/yp8oNhvyZyonUVjNkcj99L.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-article-s6",
      "text": "His family was very poor.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-article-p2",
      "tr": "他的家庭非常贫穷。",
      "g": "主语 + 系动词 + 表语",
      "d": "简单的主系表结构，描述家庭状况。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/BDZcgvpGG7eLh2aiLvmaSY.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-article-s7",
      "text": "His four grandparents stayed in the only bed in the house.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-article-p2",
      "tr": "他的四位祖父母挤在房子里唯一的一张床上。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 地点状语",
      "d": "'the only' 强调唯一性。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/tSREVpQt6jQpua2PaQx2BQ.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-article-s8",
      "text": "The family never had enough food.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-article-p2",
      "tr": "这家人从来没有足够的食物。",
      "g": "主语 + 频度副词 + 谓语 + 宾语",
      "d": "'enough' 修饰名词 'food'。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/oDQtEAf6KpBGvDhGS7rhKg.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-article-s9",
      "text": "They always ate watery cabbage soup for dinner.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-article-p2",
      "tr": "他们晚餐总是喝稀薄的卷心菜汤。",
      "g": "主语 + 频度副词 + 谓语 + 宾语 + 目的状语",
      "d": "'watery' 形容汤很稀，暗示贫穷。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/n4KRcGi4aFWyE2mNCZay2Z.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-article-s10",
      "text": "In winter, the freezing wind swept across the floor all night long.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-article-p2",
      "tr": "冬天，刺骨的寒风整夜扫过地板。",
      "g": "时间状语 + 主语 + 谓语 + 地点状语 + 时间状语",
      "d": "'swept' 是 'sweep' 的过去式。'all night long' 强调持续整夜。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/ZMGgSu6BND9Da5T3NQs2UN.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-article-s11",
      "text": "To my surprise, the family were happy together.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-article-p3",
      "tr": "令我惊讶的是，这家人在一起很幸福。",
      "g": "插入语 + 主语 + 系动词 + 表语",
      "d": "'To my surprise' 是常用插入语，表示'令我惊讶的是'。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/m2RWKVJn2ELVSQjDu7cszn.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-article-s12",
      "text": "In the evenings, Charlie sat with his grandparents in bed and listened to their stories.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-article-p3",
      "tr": "晚上，查理和祖父母一起坐在床上听他们讲故事。",
      "g": "时间状语 + 主语 + 并列谓语",
      "d": "'sat' 和 'listened' 是并列谓语，描述连续动作。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/sbAch7CNh5dtRnRzZeauRU.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-article-s13",
      "text": "Charlie’s parents often joined in.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-article-p3",
      "tr": "查理的父母也经常加入进来。",
      "g": "主语 + 频度副词 + 谓语",
      "d": "'join in' 表示'参加、加入'。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/aYnQWek4r9xYaaxab2MUDb.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-article-s14",
      "text": "Every night, the room became a happy place.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-article-p3",
      "tr": "每天晚上，这个房间都变成了一个快乐的地方。",
      "g": "时间状语 + 主语 + 系动词 + 表语",
      "d": "'became' 是系动词，后接名词作表语。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/v7Y3rEZGHZCwbQNuDik9Nh.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-article-s15",
      "text": "The whole family forgot about their hungry and poor life.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-article-p3",
      "tr": "全家人都忘记了他们饥饿和贫穷的生活。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语",
      "d": "'forget about' 意为'忘记...，不再想...'。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/63HGLyZdn8g2cvs32ycH57.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-article-s16",
      "text": "This touched me greatly.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-article-p4",
      "tr": "这深深地触动了我。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语 + 程度状语",
      "d": "'greatly' 修饰动词 'touched'，表示程度之深。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/JCvHqCKgxrwLYgaxMUugrN.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-article-s17",
      "text": "In some people’s minds, happiness comes from things like money.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-article-p4",
      "tr": "在一些人看来，幸福来自于金钱之类的东西。",
      "g": "地点状语 + 主语 + 谓语 + 来源状语",
      "d": "'come from' 表示'来自于'。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/jQT4G4MEmteLpNUSWWHrNb.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-article-s18",
      "text": "But love, in fact, is the key to happiness.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-article-p4",
      "tr": "但事实上，爱才是幸福的关键。",
      "g": "主语 + 插入语 + 系动词 + 表语",
      "d": "'the key to...' 是固定搭配，意为'...的关键'。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/TmZU2JuhNwJfoyNbA9eMmV.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-article-s19",
      "text": "Oscar Wilde once said, “Keep love in your heart. A life without it is like a sunless garden...”",
      "paragraphId": "u3-article-p4",
      "tr": "奥斯卡·王尔德曾经说过：“心中要保留爱。没有爱的生活就像一个没有阳光的花园......”",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语（直接引语）",
      "d": "引用名言来支持观点。'sunless' 由 'sun' + 后缀 'less' (无) 构成。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/m5CGM6mLV2TcViDEPfthTn.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-article-s20",
      "text": "There are so many reasons to be happy.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-article-p4",
      "tr": "有太多理由去快乐。",
      "g": "There be句型 + 不定式作定语",
      "d": "'to be happy' 修饰 'reasons'。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/SBbTuMqyjwFS6kqVcnJeah.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-article-s21",
      "text": "I think love is the most important one.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-article-p4",
      "tr": "我认为爱是最重要的一个。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语从句",
      "d": "省略了引导词 'that' 的宾语从句。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/SSrfcpiFgDXX9cJA3mTsXS.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u3-article-s22",
      "text": "It can move us, change us and give us a life full of happiness.",
      "paragraphId": "u3-article-p4",
      "tr": "它能感动我们，改变我们，给我们一个充满幸福的生活。",
      "g": "主语 + 情态动词 + 并列谓语",
      "d": "'move', 'change', 'give' 是三个并列动词原形。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/96QRrckVzd3dUHrYksrncW.mp3"
    }
  ],
